		.page__about

			// begin About
			.page__left
				h2.page__h2 Who we are
				p At TenCoins we follow the 10-C rule
			.page__right
				h3.page__about_h3 About us
				p.page__about_p We are constantly developing cutting-edge IT solutions to meet the needs of the new economy. The software developed by Tencoins targets the market of blockchain technologies, cryptocurrencies and other forms of the e-economy.

				p.page__about_p All our IT solutions combine the most modern technologies with user-friendly intuitive design. This ensures safe, convenient and unique user experience.

				p.page__about_p We use new technologies to promote decentralized principles of operation. We see blockchain as a technology that promotes transparency and trust and gives the control over the processes to each member.

				.about__h Our mission is to give financial freedom 

				h3.page__about_h3 Our vision
				p.page__about_p We believe in creating IT solutions for global, easy and modern finance available for the many people worldwide.
			// end About